name: Flock earrings
description:
Silver hoop earrings adorned with mother of pearl doves. These are by far my best selling piece, I'm guessing because they are extremely versatile and can be worn with anything from an evening gown to jeans and a t-shirt. They would also make gorgeous bridal earrings for a nature loving bride!

They measure about two inches without the earwires.

Materials:

Sterling silver
Mother of pearl

Photo by Sarah Bodri:

http://flickr.com/photos/juniper_trees/

name: Tea flower earrings
description:
Delicate Japanese tea flowers in crisp white vintage glass pop against a background of oxidized sterling. These earrings are delicate and irresistible.

They measure 1 inch including the earwire, the flower alone is half an inch.

Materials:

Oxidized sterling silver
Vintage glass

Photo by Sarah Bodri:
http://flickr.com/photos/juniper_trees/
